# Files that belong in the repo but must not be served from tutlavi.com.
# CLAUDE.md in particular was reachable at /CLAUDE.md and describes the whole
# architecture: env var names, the KV store, the admin flow.
#
# This file is only honoured for CLI deploys — a Git deployment clones the
# whole repo — so the same paths are also redirected away in vercel.json,
# which is what actually makes them unreachable in production. Keep both in
# sync if you add a file here.
CLAUDE.md
deploy-marker.txt
availability-backup.json
_menu-anim-preview.html
experiment.html

# leftovers from the Netlify host, superseded by api/
netlify.toml
netlify/
